title: Control matched for sample 1
source_name_ch1: skeletal muscle biopsy from the vastus lateralis
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted from ~5 – 10 mg of muscles using QIAGEN miRNeasy Mini Kit (Qiagen, 217004). Next generation sequencing (NGS) libraries were created using the TruSeq Stranded Total RNA library (Illumina) kit
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Next generation sequencing (NGS) libraries were created using the TruSeq Stranded Total RNA library (Illumina) kit
data_processing: Sequencing was performed on an Illumina NovaSeq 6000 instrument
data_processing.1: FASTQ generation was performed by Illumina's BaseSpace Sequence Hub
data_processing.2: Alignment of FASTQ files was performed against the GRCh37 reference by HISAT2 (v2.1.0)
data_processing.3: Gene read count abundance determined by HTSeq (v2.0)
data_processing.4: Differential expression analysis was performed by DESeq2
data_processing.5: Pathway analysis was performed using iDEP (v0.93) using the Go Biological Process gene ontology reference
data_processing.6: Differential alternative splicing events and their significance were determined by rMATS (v4.1.1)
data_processing.8: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited text files with Ensembl gene ID, gene symbol, and read counts.
data_processing.9: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited text files of skipped exon alternative splicing rMATs results
